Major changes are as follows.
1. Use the typedefs inside `<cstdint>` when implementing members of structs, classes and return type of functions.

2. Change string based message logger to stream based message logger.

#### Old
```
logger::setLogLevel(logger::LogLevel::INFO);
logger::debug("sumeragi", "This message should be hidden.");
logger::info("sumeragi", "some value: " + std::to_string(val));
```

#### New
```
logger::setLogLevel(logger::LogLevel::INFO);
logger::debug("sumeragi") << "This message should be hidden.";
logger::info("sumeragi") << "some value: " << val;
```

